```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler
    participant Loans
    participant Payments
    participant Ledger
    participant Notifications

    Scheduler->>Loans: trigger auto-debit job
    Loans->>Loans: Identify due agreements
    Loans->>Payments: initiate internal transfer (wallet debit)
    Payments->>Ledger: reserve repayment transaction
    Ledger-->>Payments: Pending entry
    Payments->>Ledger: post(transactionId)
    Ledger-->>Payments: Posted
    Payments-->>Loans: Debit success
    Loans->>Notifications: send repayment receipt
    Notifications-->>Loans: ACK
    Loans->>Scheduler: Job complete summary
```
